{"tid":657222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"汶川地震10周年　官方定5月12日為「感恩日」","createTime":"2018-05-08T02:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T11:31:09.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"d0c566e6dd1c5a80d5e1e2e4323aaabb79cba9b4","tid":657222,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:17:13.000Z","msg":"汶川大地震即將迎來10周年，汶川縣政府近日宣布將5月12日定為「感恩日」，以推動感恩教育活動。重災區之一的映秀鎮中灘堡村，該村支部書記楊雲兵表示，地震發生後，來自全國各地的人都為鎮的搶險救援和災後重建付出巨大心血，「全國大愛匯聚這裏才有了映秀的今天，我們不能忘記」。<br />\n<br />\n2008年5月12日，四川汶川縣發生黎克特制8.2級大地震，造成近7萬人死亡，超過37萬人受傷。重災區映秀鎮內的逾萬名居民，更有半數以上死亡及失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n幾時好似吉之島 一田咁整個感謝祭?<br />\n支那又白事當紅事做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d96194309da8bc47bf2715a17688fe076ea24e","tid":657222,"uid":103207,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:18:01.000Z","msg":"感謝祭? 我諗到sod<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc48299f8c5833fed20dd99139cdb4777d976b6","tid":657222,"uid":122,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:18:37.000Z","msg":"[回帶] 四川女官員「你們說捐獻，我們沒看見啊！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/352908/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/352908/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f61047a270cede70924f84484a393958f78fae40","tid":657222,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:29:29.000Z","msg":"thanksgiving<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13de6a205a5813f30c585650eac05ccd52086a58","tid":657222,"uid":65686,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:33:40.000Z","msg":"希望領導死嘅時候都要感謝納稅人養住你哋兒女。"},{"pid":"548ae27140132f98541099862eccf999da871352","tid":657222,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:34:42.000Z","msg":"個時捐撚左100 屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76